            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Pamela, do you have a minute?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, why hello there Sophie. What do you need?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Um, this is hard to explain, but... What do you think you should do to restore the memories of someone who's lost them?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Memories? Let's see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I think the best way is to give them a biiig shock."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "A shock...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes. For example, you could use a wooden pole to bonk them on the head."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "U-um, I think if you did that, they would lose even more memories..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, was that idea no good...?"
